```plantuml
@startuml OpenRoberta_robertalab-ev3dev
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #f9f9f9
  BorderColor #2c3e50
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

package "Open Roberta Lab EV3 Connector" {
  rectangle "Brickman UI\n(DBus)" as UI #f0f8ff
  rectangle "roberta.lab.Service\n(DBus Service)" as Service #add8e6
  rectangle "roberta.lab.Connector\n(Network Communication)" as Connector #b0e0e6
  rectangle "roberta.ev3.Hal\n(Hardware Abstraction)" as Hal #afeeee
  rectangle "roberta.lab.AbortHandler\n(Key Press Monitor)" as AbortHandler #b0c4de
  rectangle "roberta.lab.GfxMode\n(Graphics Mode Manager)" as GfxMode #d3d3d3
  rectangle "ev3dev.auto\n(EV3 Hardware Library)" as ev3dev #f5f5dc
}

UI <--> Service : DBus Communication
Service <--> Connector : Manage Connection
Connector --> UI : Execute Code
Connector --> Hal : Control Hardware
Hal --> ev3dev : Interact with EV3
AbortHandler --> Service : Abort Signal
GfxMode --> Service : Manage Display

@enduml
```